title: boards 292 what should my cet score be for below <500 rank
content:
please help if anyone has any legit data from last year

comments.body: It depends on the difficulty of the paper..

This was in 2022

I had got 150+ few years back with 295 on board. Rank was  1001. 
So it depends on paper.
